<br>
This was back in 2001.  Now, in 2003, today's exchange rate is....<br>
<br>
1$ US = .8963 Euro<br>
(just for more dramatic effect.... back in 2000, 1$ us = 1.4 British pounds, now it's 1$ US = 1.7 British Pounds)<br>
